  <section class="closing">
    <h2>Open Signpost first, then layer in the rest.</h2>
    <p>Start with one route source of truth. Add the other apps only when they solve a real planning gap.</p>
    <a class="primary-cta" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/og/road-signpost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open Road Signpost</a>
  </section>
</div>
